{"title_page": "Facundo P\u00e9rez", "text_new": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Facundo P\u00e9rez\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| caption = \n| fullname = Facundo Mart\u00edn P\u00e9rez\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1999|7|31|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Quilmes]], Argentina\n| height = 1.70m\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas|Lan\u00fas]]\n| clubnumber = 34\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas|Lan\u00fas]]\n| years1 = 2020\u2013     | clubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas|Lan\u00fas]] | caps1 = 4 | goals1 = 0\n| club-update = 22 March 2020\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Facundo Mart\u00edn P\u00e9rez''' (born 31 July 1999) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas|Lan\u00fas]].\n\n==Professional career==\nP\u00e9rez made his professional debut for Lan\u00fas in a 2-0 [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] win over [[Godoy Cruz Antonio Tomba|Godoy Cruz]] on 2 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2020/02/02/argentina/primera-division/ca-lanus/godoy-cruz-antonio-tomba/3070529/|title=Lan\u00fas vs. Godoy Cruz - 2 February 2020 - Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|facundo-perez/621375}}\n\n{{Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Perez, Facundo}}\n[[Category:1999 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Quilmes]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Facundo P\u00e9rez\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| caption = \n| fullname = Facundo Mart\u00edn P\u00e9rez\n| birth_date = {