{"title_page": "Mariano Peralta Bauer", "text_new": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Mariano Peralta Bauer\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| caption = \n| fullname = Mariano Peralta Bauer\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1998|2|20|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Adrogu\u00e9]], Argentina\n| height = 1.80m\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub = [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]]\n| clubnumber = 17\n| youthyears1 = 2007\u20132020 | youthclubs1 = [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]]\n| years1 = 2020\u2013     | clubs1 = [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]] | caps1 = 2 | goals1 = 0\n| club-update = 22 March 2020\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Mariano Peralta Bauer''' (born 20 February 1998) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]].\n\n==Professional career==\nOn 11 September 2018, Peralta Bauer signed his first professional contract with [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://vamosciclon.com/san-lorenzo/mariano-peralta-bauer-firmo-su-primer-contrato-profesional-con-san-lorenzo/|title=Peralta Bauer firm\u00f3 su primer contrato profesional|first=Vamos|last=Cicl\u00f3n|date=September 11, 2018|website=Vamos Cicl\u00f3n}}</ref> He made his professional debut with San Lorenzo in a 3-1 [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] win over [[Aldosivi]] on 1 March 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2020/03/01/argentina/primera-division/club-atletico-aldosivi/club-atletico-san-lorenzo-de-almagro/3070577/|title=Aldosivi vs. San Lorenzo - 1 March 2020 - Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|mariano-peralta-bauer/648145}}\n* [https://www.sanlorenzo.com.ar/futbol-amateur/reserva/plantel/perfil/mariano-peraltabauer?p=1 San Lorenzo Profile]\n\n{{San Lorenzo squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Peralta Bauer, Mariano}}\n[[Category:1998 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Adrogu\u00e9]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:San Lorenzo footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Mariano Peralta Bauer\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| caption = \n| fullname = Mariano Peralta Bauer\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1998|2|20|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Adrogu\u00e9]], Argentina\n| height = 1.80m\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub = [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]]\n| clubnumber = 17\n| youthyears1 = 2007\u20132020 | youthclubs1 = [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]]\n| years1 = 2020\u2013     | clubs1 = [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]] | caps1 = 2 | goals1 = 0\n| club-update = 22 March 2020\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Mariano Peralta Bauer''' (born 20 February 1998) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]].\n\n==Professional career==\nOn 11 September 2018, Peralta Bauer signed his first professional contract with [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://vamosciclon.com/san-lorenzo/mariano-peralta-bauer-firmo-su-primer-contrato-profesional-con-san-lorenzo/|title=Peralta Bauer firm\u00f3 su primer contrato profesional|first=Vamos|last=Cicl\u00f3n|date=September 11, 2018|website=Vamos Cicl\u00f3n}}</ref> He made his professional debut with San Lorenzo in a 3-1 [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] win over [[Aldosivi]] on 1 March 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2020/03/01/argentina/primera-division/club-atletico-aldosivi/club-atletico-san-lorenzo-de-almagro/3070577/|title=Aldosivi vs. San Lorenzo - 1 March 2020 - Soccerway|web