irlines-wins-top-indian-ocean-carrier-spot-at-world-travel-awards-25211/|archive-date=25 October 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|[[Vistara]]| [[Indira Gandhi International Airport|Delhi]]|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.financialexpress.com/lifestyle/travel-tourism/vistara-announces-daily-direct-flights-between-delhi-thiruvananthapuram-check-fares-schedule/1737322/|title=Vistara announces daily direct flights between Delhi, Thiruvananthapuram; check fares, schedule|date=16 October 2019|accessdate=10 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125063830/https://www.financialexpress.com/lifestyle/travel-tourism/vistara-announces-daily-direct-flights-between-delhi-thiruvananthapuram-check-fares-schedule/1737322/|archive-date=25 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n}}\n\n{| class=\"collapsible collapsed\" style=\"border:1px #aaa solid; width:50em; margin:0.2em auto\"\n|-\n! Destinations map\n|-\n|{{Location map+ |Asia |width=1000 |float=center\n|caption=Destinations from Trivandrum International Airport <br /> ({{font color | red | Red}}) = Year-round Destination <br />({{font color | green | Green }}) = Seasonal Destination <br /> ({{font color | blue | Blue }}) = Future Destination\n|places=\n{{Location map~ |Asia |lat=10.1518|long=76.3930|position=left|label='''<small>Trivandrum</small>'''|caption=|mark=Airplane_silhouette.svg | marksize=15 }}\n{{Location map~ |Asia |lat=25.3284|long=55.5123|position=right|label='''<small>[[Sharjah International Airport|Sharjah]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |Asia |lat=2.7456|long=101.7072|position=top|label='''<small>[[Kuala Lumpur International Airport|Kuala Lampur]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |Asia |lat=13.1986|long=77.7066|position=left|label='''<small>[[Kempegowda International Airport|Bengaluru]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7}}\n{{Location map~ |Asia |lat=28.5562|long=77.1000|position=top |label='''<small>[[Indira Gandhi International Airport|Delhi]